    <div class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> We answer our own emails</div>
    <div class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> Replies sent from London</div>
    <div class="ticker-item"><span>✦</span> No carrier pigeons (yet)</div>
  </div>
</div>

